    <note caller="[b]" style="f">
      <char style="fk">[b]</char>
      <char style="ft"><char style="it">in close contact with</char>…Lit: <char style="it">with</char>. Same usage of the word
        <char style="it">with</char> as John used in the phrase <char style="it">the Concept was with God </char>(John
        1:1).</char>
